and record keeping.

00:02:01.583 --> 00:02:03.504
And overall, they do a pretty good job.

00:02:03.528 --> 00:02:05.225
But there are growing problems.

00:02:05.942 --> 00:02:07.474
To begin, they're centralized.

00:02:07.498 --> 00:02:10.466
That means they can be hacked,
and increasingly are --

00:02:10.490 --> 00:02:13.049
JP Morgan, the US Federal Government,

00:02:13.073 --> 00:02:14.864
LinkedIn, Home Depot and others

00:02:14.888 --> 00:02:16.303
found that out the hard way.

00:02:16.874 --> 00:02:20.388
They exclude billions of people
from the global economy,

00:02:20.412 --> 00:02:22.665
for example, people
who don't have enough money

00:02:22.689 --> 00:02:23.949
to have a bank account.

00:02:24.624 --> 00:02:26.912
They slow things down.

00:02:26.936 --> 00:02:30.506
